  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate the ability to reduce the number of OR personnel
      required while performing the following procedures: colon resections, cholecystectomies and
      anti-reflux/hiatal hernia surgery with the AutoLap system compared with the standard
      operation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
